lu_part1: Et ass net alles Gold wat blénkt
lu_part2: an net alles Dreck wat sténkt.
en_literal_translation_p1: Not all that glitters is gold
en_literal_translation_p2: and not all that stinks is dirt.
en_closest_real_corresponding_saying_p1: All that glitters is not gold
en_closest_real_corresponding_saying_p2: and not everything foul is worthless.
